nk"></span></button></span></h3><p>PETRA table &amp; column: real_estate.RE=
E_S_REAL_ESTATE_TYPE</p><pre><code class=3D"language-json">    [
        "ApartmentHouseLiving", // -&gt; MultiFamilyHouse
        "ApartmentHouseMixed", // -&gt; MixedUseRealEstate
        "BusinessProperty", // -&gt; CommercialRealEstate
        "GGL1", // -&gt; MixedUseRealEstate
        "GGL2", // -&gt; MixedUseRealEstate
        "HomeFloor",    // -&gt; SingleFamilyHouse
        "HomeHouse",    // -&gt; SingleFamilyHouse
        "Unknown"   // -&gt; Unknown
    ]
</code></pre><p>Proposal</p><pre><code class=3D"language-json">    [
        {"0": "Unknown"},
        {"1": "SingleFamilyHouse"}, // Einfamilienhaus
        {"2": "MultiFamilyHouse"}, // Mehrfamilienhaus
        {"3": "Condominium"} // Eigentumswohnung
        {"4": "CommercialRealEstate"}, // Kommerzielle Liegenschaften
        {"5": "MixedUseRealEstate"}, // Gemischt genutzte Liegenschaften
        {"6": "Others"} // =C3=BCbribe Immobilien, angefangene Bauten und B=
auland
    ]  =20
</code></pre><h5 id=3D"MortgageLogicalModel-ReasoningStefan">Reasoning Stef=
an<span class=3D"copy-heading-link-container"><button class=3D"copy-heading=
-link-button" aria-label=3D"Copy link to heading" data-heading-id=3D"Mortga=
